      "updated": 1783887250973,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Imagine you are a technical recruiter and you have an interview in a few minutes.\nWhat questions will you ask?\nYou spot a candidate's GitHub on the CV and find an active side project there!\n\nYou use CodeSparks and in a moment you have a number of questions and talking points!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Imagine you are a technical recruiter and you have an interview in a few minutes.\nWhat questions will you ask?\nYou spot a candidate's GitHub on the CV and find an active side project there!\n\nYou use CodeSparks and in a moment you have a number of questions and talking points!",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
