      ],
      "updated": 1783890693007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In AD 2600 the human race is finally beginning to realize its full\npotential. Hundreds of colonized planets scattered across the galaxy\nhost a multitude of prosperous and wildly diverse cultures. Genetic\nengineering has pushed evolution far beyond nature's boundaries,\ndefeating disease and producing extraordinary spaceborn creatures.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In AD 2600 the human race is finally beginning to realize its full potential. Hundreds of colonized planets scattered across the galaxy host a multitude of prosperous and wildly diverse cultures. Genetic engineering has pushed evolution far beyond nature's boundaries, defeating disease and producing extraordinary spaceborn creatures.",
